AI Engineer Skill Map Venn Diagram. Three overlapping circles: 1) Machine Learning / Deep Learning (Models, Training, Eval), 2) Software Engineering (Architecture, CI/CD, Testing), 3) Product / Business (User Needs, Metrics, ROI). Center overlap: AI ENGINEER. Skills radiating from each: ML: PyTorch, Transformers, MLOps; SE: APIs, System Design, Prompt Eng; Product: Eval, Cost Opt, UX. Professional Venn diagram, German labels.